text: Matt Pinnell (born August 15, 1979) is an American Republican politician. He is the 17th lieutenant governor of Oklahoma, since 2019. Pinnell is also the first Oklahoma Secretary of Tourism & Branding. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Lieutenant Governors of Oklahoma Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Dallas Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Enid, Oklahoma
